  Locus:
    Page: 143
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Failure/Mistake
---
It is defeat that turns bone to flint and gristle to muscle, and makes
men invincible. ... Do not then be afraid of defeat. You are never so near
victory as when defeated in a good cause.
